message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Insomnia"
abstract: "Lightweight Windows utility that prevents your PC from sleeping while AI coding tools (Claude Code, Cursor, Aider, OpenAI Codex, Ollama) or watched applications are running. Uses hook-based integration for precise activity detection — awake while the tool works, asleep within 3 minutes after it stops."
